{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-remark-js","path":"/hitchhikers-guide/apps/docs/cluster-scope/add_user_to_group.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"eb75f28b-1dad-50ce-b57e-859cf3b25396","html":"<h1 id=\"adding-user-to-an-ocp-team\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-user-to-an-ocp-team\" aria-label=\"adding user to an ocp team permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding User to an OCP team</h1>\n<p>All user groups can be found <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/apps/tree/master/cluster-scope/base/user.openshift.io/groups\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>Find the folder that corresponds with your group and append the <code class=\"language-text\">group.yaml</code> file within that directory.</p>\n<h1 id=\"making-a-user-cluster-admin\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#making-a-user-cluster-admin\" aria-label=\"making a user cluster admin permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Making a user cluster admin</h1>\n<p>Cluster admins are handled on a per-cluster basis.</p>\n<p>To add a user as a cluster admin for a particular cluster, add the GitHub handle associated with that user to this file\n<code class=\"language-text\">cluster-scope/overlays/prod/${ENV}/${CLUSTER}/groups/cluster-admins.yaml</code>.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/apps/blob/master/docs/cluster-scope/add_user_to_group.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null,"extraClasses":null,"banner":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"eb75f28b-1dad-50ce-b57e-859cf3b25396"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","1764348645","3000541721","3606484676"]}